data.description: Welcome to this warm and inviting single-family home located in a prime location close to the base. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms, this charming property offers the perfect space for comfortable living. Step inside to discover a cozy and inviting atmosphere, with a spacious living area that is perfect for relaxation and entertainment. With a carport for your vehicles, this home provides both convenience and practicality. Don't miss the opportunity to make this home yours today.
